			      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
				        <ab>(This) <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">āyaka</foreign> pillar
					(is) the pious gift of the housewife Utaradatā (Uttaradattā)
					Sidhathamitā (Siddhārthamitrā), the wife of the <foreign xml:lang="pra-Latn">mahānāvika</foreign> Sivaka
